title: Golden Rickshaw Take Away
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chinese restaurant catering to vegans (has a sign on door). Offers different tofu and vegetable dishes with rice. Vegan items are not indicated on the menu, but the staff can help you in choosing within the tofu or vegetable dishes. Online ordering available.
